org.gvsig.raster.impl.datastruct

Class GeoPointImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.raster.impl.datastruct.GeoPointImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeoPoint

    public class GeoPointImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements GeoPoint
    This class represents a ground control point which can be associated to a raster. This kind of points has information about real and pixel coordinates and other information like RMS errors related to it.
